            "pub_date": "2025-12-04 17:10:37",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "融創中國11月合同銷售按年跌逾30% 今年累計跌幅超過25%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">融創中國(01918)公布，今年11月實現合同銷售約11.2億元(人民幣．下同)，較去年同期的16.1億元減少30.43%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：融創中國官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20230905_FI_source-web_01918_SUNAC_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：融創中國官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20230905_FI_source-web_01918_SUNAC_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：融創中國官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上述合同銷售涉及樓面約9.2萬平方米，均價約每平方米1.217萬元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今年以來累計實現合同銷售為338.9億元，較去年同期的453.9億元減少25.34%；涉及樓面118.1萬平方米，均價每平方米約2.87萬元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15480465-%e8%9e%8d%e5%89%b5%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b11%e6%9c%88%e5%90%88%e5%90%8c%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be30-%e4%bb%8a%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%af%e8%a8%88%e8%b7%8c%e5%b9%85%e8%b6%85%e9%81%8e25",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/01918-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-04 17:10:40",
